{
  "texts": [
    "GPT-4 has the potential to improve the writing process for instructors and students by providing instant feedback on grammar, syntax, and coherence, and by suggesting revisions that enhance the clarity and effectiveness of written texts (Arif et al., 2023).",
    "Such tools may also help writers generate ideas, brainstorm, and organize their thoughts; this ability will likely save time and effort, and improve the overall quality of writing (Liebrenz et al., 2023).",
    "Islam and Islam (2023) have suggested that ChatGPT will improve innovation and creativity by automating tasks (e.g., data collection, literature reviews) allowing researchers to focus their energy on higher level tasks.",
    "ChatGPT may also help researchers be better informed by summarizing the literature based on any specific topic.",
    "Furthermore, ChatGPT has the potential to deliver real-time insights into the rapidly evolving realm of technology."
  ]
}